Code: EXEC SQL SELECT NUM_APOL_SINISTRO FROM SEGUROS.SI_DETALHE_PROC_JURID WHERE T1.COD_OPERACAO IN (8300,8301,8302,8303,8304,8305) AND T1.NUM_APOL_SINISTRO = :SI9HR001.NUM_APOL_SINISTRO AND T1.COD_PROCESSO_JURID = :SI9HR001.COD_PROCESSO_JURID AND T1.DTH_CADASTRAMENTO <= (SELECT MAX(T2.DTH_TIMESTAMP) FROM SEGUROS.SI_PROCESSO_JURID T2 WHERE T2.NUM_APOL_SINISTRO = T1.NUM_APOL_SINISTRO AND T2.COD_PROCESSO_JURID = T1.COD_PROCESSO_JURID) END SQL
